29.29.text:
If Donald Trump doesn’t secure a seat in
the White House, at least there will be a

33.99.text:
seat for him in the bathroom. A bathroom fixture
company in Shenzhen South China, known as

38.47.text:
Shenzhen Trump Industries, have actually created
a Trump toilet seat, however, not just any

44.42.text:
old toilet seat but a luxury one with self-changing
seat protectors available in both green and

50.93.text:
blue. The company has no affiliation with
Trump but continues to produce Trump toilet

55.38.text:
seats as well as other bathroom fixtures for
venues such as spas and hotels. If you think

60.29.text:
a Trump toilet seat is bizarre, you can even
purchase some Donald Trump toilet paper, which

64.92.text:
is an actual thing! There are companies out
there which sell toilet roll with Donald Trump’s

70.23.text:
face printed on each sheet. You can let Donald’s
smug face kiss your ass or maybe even use

77.21.text:
it for some other purpose but one thing is
clear, it is the perfect way to show Donald

81.63.text: how you really feel about him.

83.07.text: Number 4 – Donald Trump Cat Scratching Post

85.52.text:
If you are not too much of a fan of Donald
Trump yourself then you can even let your

88.88.text:
pet cat share your hate with a Donald Trump
Cat Scratching Post. A Canadian company who

93.47.text:
design these products have a Kickstarter campaign
named “Politikats” and create politically

99.03.text:
inclined cat scratching posts not just focussed
on Donald Trump but on other presidential

103.76.text:
candidates too including Vladimir Putin. According
to Politikat’s Facebook page the scratching

109.08.text:
posts are designed to “enhance the beauty
of your home”. Sure your cat might not be

114.03.text:
interested in political affairs but I assure
you that your cat will be interested in scratching

122.21.text:
If you are very much a huge supporter of Trump
then you maybe you can show your affection

128.19.text:
with this Donald Trump Butt Plug and get some
pleasure in the process. However, for the

133.09.text:
creator of this product it was designed as
an insult towards Trump after Trump’s remarks

137.41.text:
towards Mexicans and Latinos. Mexican born
artist, Fernando Sosa was angry and insulted

143.62.text:
at Trump’s immigration rhetoric directed
at Mexicans saying that, “Mexico is sending

148.49.text:
‘rapists’ and drug dealers to the United
States”. In the product listing, Sosa explained

153.64.text:
that, “I usually make Butt plugs to insult
dictators, homophobes, and politicians. However,

158.58.text:
when I heard Donald Trump's remarks about
Mexicans and Latinos from South America I

162.73.text:
was extremely angry.” The Butt plug is created
using 3D printing technology, made from full-colour

168.39.text:
sandstone promising “a course finish and
a delicate feel.”

182.03.text:
Although not intended to be a Donald Trump-inspired
product, you can’t deny that it bears an

187.35.text:
uncanny resemblance to Donald Trump’s golden
hair. Referred by the public as Trump’s

192.81.text:
hair, these “Princetown” Goat-Hair Mule
slippers were actually made by the luxury

197.81.text:
fashion company, Gucci and cost a staggering
$1800! These luxury slippers were hailed as

205.55.text:
a “bold new trend”, however, I am not
quite so sure about that… You are pretty

210.51.text:
much walking with Donald Trump’s hair on
your feet. Although highly expensive, the

215.78.text:
company does offer free shipping which I guess
is a bonus.

227.00.text:
If you are of Mexican or Latino origin then
this is the perfect way to release your anger

233.96.text:
and hit back at Donald Trump literally for
his comments about Mexicans and Latinos. The

238.46.text:
piñata was designed by piñata maker, Dalton
Ramirez, who was outraged by Trump’s remarks

244.66.text:
about immigrants. Retailing for around $40,
the piñatas were a hit in in Mexico and parts

251.14.text:
of the US and sellers are having trouble keeping
up with demand. Even a shop in Portland, Oregon

256.68.text:
invited a group of people, mostly children,
to destroy a human-sized Trump piñata at

261.66.text:
their grand opening. The children and adults,
predominantly Latinos, took it in turns beating

267.06.text:
the Trump piñata with a baseball bat. If
you have great disdain for Trump then this

271.57.text:
may be a worthy investment for you to let
off some steam and relieve some stress.
